'''伪枝藻素'''（{{lang-en|Scytonemin}}）是一种[[生物色素|生物色素]]，由许多[[藍菌門|藍细菌]]合成，包括''Calothrix sp.''<ref>{{cite journal |pages=484–91|doi=10.1046/j.1462-2920.2003.00436.x |title=The synthesis of the UV-screening pigment, scytonemin, and photosynthetic performance in isolates from closely related natural populations of cyanobacteria (Calothrix sp.) |year=2003 |last1=Dillon |first1=Jesse G. |last2=Castenholz |first2=Richard W. |journal=Environmental Microbiology |volume=5 |issue=6 |pmid=12755715}}</ref>、''Lyngbya aestuarii''<ref name=pmid21501195>{{cite journal |pages=1–11 |doi=10.1111/j.1574-6941.2011.01113.x |title=The biosynthesis of cyanobacterial sunscreen scytonemin in intertidal microbial mat communities |year=2011 |last1=Balskus |first1=Emily P. |last2=Case |first2=Rebecca J. |last3=Walsh |first3=Christopher T. |journal=FEMS Microbiology Ecology}}</ref>等，最早在1849被人发现，但直到1993年才解析了其结构<ref name=pmid8405307>{{cite journal |pages=825–9 |doi=10.1007/BF01923559 |title=The structure of scytonemin, an ultraviolet sunscreen pigment from the sheaths of cyanobacteria |year=1993 |last1=Proteau |first1=P. J. |last2=Gerwick |first2=W. H. |last3=Garcia-Pichel |first3=F. |last4=Castenholz |first4=R. |journal=Experientia |volume=49 |issue=9 |pmid=8405307}}</ref>。据信，伪枝藻素对细菌起到了[[防曬油|防曬油]]的作用，在325-425 nm的有很大的吸收峰，并在250 nm的紫外波段有个独立的吸收峰<ref name=pmid8405307/>，在暴露在[[紫外线|紫外线]]的情况下才启动它的[[生物合成|生物合成]]<ref>{{cite journal |pages=159–72 |doi=10.1039/A815159Y |title=Mycosporines: are they nature’s sunscreens? |year=1998 |last1=M. Bandaranayake |first1=Wickramasinghe |journal=Natural Product Reports |volume=15 |issue=2 |pmid=9586224}}</ref>。

==生物合成==
在 ''Lyngbya aestuarii'' 体内的伪枝藻素生物合成途径最近由 Balskus、Case和Walsh 发现。它起始于L-[[色氨酸|色氨酸]]到[[3-吲哚丙酮酸|3-吲哚丙酮酸]]的转化，之后再与[[4-羟苯丙酮酸|对羟基苯丙酮酸]]结合。产物的β-酮酸基 再发生环化形成带羰基的三环化合物，之后再氧化二聚化形成伪枝藻素，三个反应步骤依次由ScyB、ScyA、ScyC催化，如下图所示<ref name=pmid21501195/>：
